methods.name: public Object get(ULocale locale)
methods.comment:
* Convenience override for callers using locales.  This calls
     * get(ULocale, int, ULocale[]) with KIND_ANY for kind and null for
     * actualReturn.

methods.name: public Object get(ULocale locale, int kind)
methods.comment:
* Convenience override for callers using locales.  This calls
     * get(ULocale, int, ULocale[]) with a null actualReturn.

methods.name: public Object get(ULocale locale, ULocale[] actualReturn)
methods.comment:
* Convenience override for callers using locales.  This calls
     * get(ULocale, int, ULocale[]) with KIND_ANY for kind.

methods.name: public Object get(ULocale locale, int kind, ULocale[] actualReturn)
methods.comment:
* Convenience override for callers using locales.  This uses
     * createKey(ULocale.toString(), kind) to create a key, calls getKey, and then
     * if actualReturn is not null, returns the actualResult from
     * getKey (stripping any prefix) into a ULocale.

methods.name: public Factory registerObject(Object obj, ULocale locale)
methods.comment:
* Convenience override for callers using locales.  This calls
     * registerObject(Object, ULocale, int kind, boolean visible)
     * passing KIND_ANY for the kind, and true for the visibility.

methods.name: public Factory registerObject(Object obj, ULocale locale, boolean visible)
methods.comment:
* Convenience override for callers using locales.  This calls
     * registerObject(Object, ULocale, int kind, boolean visible)
     * passing KIND_ANY for the kind.

methods.name: public Factory registerObject(Object obj, ULocale locale, int kind)
methods.comment:
* Convenience function for callers using locales.  This calls
     * registerObject(Object, ULocale, int kind, boolean visible)
     * passing true for the visibility.

methods.name: public Factory registerObject(Object obj, ULocale locale, int kind, boolean visible)
methods.comment:
* Convenience function for callers using locales.  This  instantiates
     * a SimpleLocaleKeyFactory, and registers the factory.

methods.name: public Locale[] getAvailableLocales()
methods.comment:
* Convenience method for callers using locales.  This returns the standard
     * Locale list, built from the Set of visible ids.

methods.name: public ULocale[] getAvailableULocales()
methods.comment:
* Convenience method for callers using locales.  This returns the standard
     * ULocale list, built from the Set of visible ids.

methods.name: public String validateFallbackLocale()
methods.comment:
* Return the name of the current fallback locale.  If it has changed since this was
     * last accessed, the service cache is cleared.
